data.description: CROSS CREEK Location!  Situated on 1.18 acres this property boasts an expansive, covered wrap around porch.. perfect place to sit and take in the peaceful surroundings. Inside you will be greeted by a nice entry way which flows perfectly into the gourmet kitchen complete with cherry cabinets, double ovens, gas cook top, and tons of STORAGE/Countertop Space.  The family is room located just off the kitchen as well as a dining area, laundry, and full size bath. Main level is complete with a full size bedroom with half bath and additional room that could be used as an office. Upper level features the primary suite, two more bedrooms and full size bath. The HUGE Rec room is the perfect place to gather with family and friends surrounded by the POOL TABLE that will stay and includes an additional finished room off of the Rec room.  There is plenty of parking and work space in the oversized three car garage!  HUGE home conveniently located to Marion!
